  <h1> Why Use Coffee Nerd? </h1>
  <div>
    <p class="paragraph">
      Coffee Nerd is written for those who appreciate paying attention to detail and those who desire to savor a cup of coffee.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here is the short of it.  Coffee Nerd strives to help the home coffee brewer brew an excellent cup of coffee by stressing three factors.  First, accurate, consistent measuresments.  You really need a ktichen scale for this.  At home, I use an  <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Ozeri-ZK14-S-Digital-Multifunction-Kitchen/dp/B004164SRA/ref=asc_df_B004164SRA/?tag=hyprod-20&linkCode=df0&hvadid=167142021489&hvpos=1o1&hvnetw=g&hvrand=5979156706348560214&hvpone=&hvptwo=&hvqmt=&hvdev=c&hvdvcmdl=&hvlocint=&hvlocphy=9001975&hvtargid=pla-113282083020&psc=1" target="_blank">Ozeri ZK14-S</a>.  Second, the water to coffee ratio plays a key role.  The app will help with this!  Third, the grind size can make all of the difference in the world.  At home, I use a <a href="https://www.capresso.com/coffee-grinders/infinity-conical-burr-grinder-stainless-finish.html" target="_blank">Capresso</a> Infinity Conical Burr Ginder.
    </p>
    <p>
      This app offers you, the coffee enthusiast, the ability to select a brewing method, track a coffee, and input the number of servings.  The app will in turn provide you with the amount of water to use, the amount of coffee to use and the desired grind size.
    </p>
